title: 'Unprecedented': U.S. Repatriates over 25,000 Stranded Americans During Coronavirus Pandemic
description: The Trump administration is working to repatriate "an additional 9,000" American citizens stranded overseas because of the coronavirus global pandemic after helping over 25,000 return home, a State Department official revealed on Monday.
